### Create page in workspace
POST http://localhost:6767/page
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Project Roadmap",
    "icon": ":D",
    "content": "# Roadmap\n\n## Q1 Goals\n- Launch MVP\n- Onboard 10 users",
    "workspace": "WORKSPACE_ID_HERE"
}

###

### Create sub-page (nested under parent)
POST http://localhost:6767/page
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Q1 Details",
    "content": "Detailed breakdown of Q1 goals...",
    "workspace": "WORKSPACE_ID_HERE",
    "parent": "PARENT_PAGE_ID_HERE"
}

###

### Get all pages in workspace (top-level)
GET http://localhost:6767/page?workspace=WORKSPACE_ID_HERE

###

### Get page by ID
GET http://localhost:6767/page/PAGE_ID_HERE

###

### Update page
PUT http://localhost:6767/page/PAGE_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Updated Roadmap",
    "icon": ":P",
    "content": "# Updated content\n\nNew roadmap details here..."
}

###

### Update page cover image
PUT http://localhost:6767/page/PAGE_ID_HERE/cover
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "coverImage": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dvdf6c1vv/image/upload/v1234/cover.jpg"
}

###

### Move page to different parent
PUT http://localhost:6767/page/PAGE_ID_HERE/move
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "parent": "NEW_PARENT_PAGE_ID_HERE"
}

###

### Move page to top-level (remove parent)
PUT http://localhost:6767/page/PAGE_ID_HERE/move
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "parent": null
}

###

### Archive page
PUT http://localhost:6767/page/PAGE_ID_HERE/archive

###

### Unarchive page
PUT http://localhost:6767/page/PAGE_ID_HERE/unarchive

###

### Toggle favorite
PUT http://localhost:6767/page/PAGE_ID_HERE/favorite

###

### Delete page
DELETE http://localhost:6767/page/PAGE_ID_HERE
